  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Beefalo Wool/DST</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Beefalo Wool</b> is an <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Item\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Item\">Item</a> obtained by killing a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Beefalo\" title=\"Beefalo\">Beefalo</a> or聽a聽<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Baby_Beefalo\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Baby Beefalo\">Baby Beefalo</a>, by shaving a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sleeping\" title=\"Sleeping\">sleeping</a>聽Beefalo with a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Razor\" title=\"Razor\">Razor</a> (by clicking them with a Razor held by the mouse cursor), or using a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Brush\" title=\"Brush\">Brush</a> on a Beefalo.聽It is used to make a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Saddle\" title=\"Saddle\">Saddle</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Winter_Hat\" title=\"Winter Hat\">Winter Hat</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Beefalo_Hat\" title=\"Beefalo Hat\">Beefalo Hat</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Puffy_Vest\" title=\"Puffy Vest\">Puffy Vest</a>, and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Carpeted_Flooring\" title=\"Carpeted Flooring\">Carpeted Flooring</a>.\n</p><p>Beefalo Wool also makes an excellent <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fuel\" title=\"Fuel\">Fuel</a> source for <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Campfire\" title=\"Campfire\">Campfires</a> and Fire Pits. A small herd of Beefalo can easily keep a Fire Pit lit for days, and as the wool grows back, this is a good short term solution.\nThere are alternative methods of obtaining Beefalo Wool; harvesting a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tumbleweed\" title=\"Tumbleweed\">Tumbleweed</a>, or befriending a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Catcoon\" title=\"Catcoon\">Catcoon</a>, as friendly Catcoons may give Beefalo Wool as a gift.\n</p><p><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Willow\" title=\"Willow\">Willow</a> needs Beefalo Wool to craft <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bernie\" title=\"Bernie\">Bernie</a>. It is also required to craft <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lures\" title=\"Lures\">Spinnerbait Lures</a> and to complete the construction of the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Royal_Tapestry\" title=\"Royal Tapestry\">Royal Tapestry</a>.\n</p><p>Beefalo Wool can be crafted by Wilson if he got &quot;<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Transmute_Icky_II\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Transmute Icky II\">Transmute Icky II</a>&quot;\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Tools\" title=\"Icon Tools\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Beefalo_Wool\" title=\"Beefalo Wool\"><img alt=\"Beefalo Wool.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Beefalo_Wool.png?a13eb8\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>脳<b>4</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pig_Skin\" title=\"Pig Skin\"><img alt=\"Pig Skin.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pig_Skin.png?3a7624\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>脳<b>4</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Gold_Nugget\" title=\"Gold Nugget\"><img alt=\"Gold Nugget.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Gold_Nugget.png?f67236\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>脳<b>4</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Alchemy_Engine\" title=\"Alchemy Engine\"><img alt=\"Alchemy Engine.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Alchemy_Engine.png/42px-Alc