//dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Beefalo_Shrine.png/42px-Beefalo_Shrine.png?d945dc\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Judge%27s_Booth_Item\" title=\"Judge&#x27;s Booth Item\"><img alt=\"Judge&#x27;s Booth.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Judge%27s_Booth.png?c8d328\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>Only during <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Year_of_the_Beefalo\" title=\"Year of the Beefalo\">Year of the Beefalo</a> event</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Beefalo Wool is apparently what <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tallbird_Nest\" title=\"Tallbird Nest\">Tallbird Nests</a> are made out of, according to <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Maxwell_(Character)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maxwell (Character)\">Maxwell&#x27;s</a> examination quote. (&quot;It&#x27;s made of dirty beefalo hair.&quot;)</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:CD_beefalowool.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\"><img alt=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/CD_beefalowool.png/120px-CD_beefalowool.png?5d10ca\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/CD_Don%27t_Starve\" title=\"CD Don&#x27;t Starve\">CD Don&#x27;t Starve</a>.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Resources-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Beefalo_Wool/DST#Resources-0\">Resources</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Craftable_Items-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Beefalo_Wool/DST#Craftable_Items-0\">Craftable Items</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
