  "plainText": "Don't Starve\nTogether\nBeefalo Wool\nObject Info\n45 sec.\nCan be Burned\n40\nSource\nDropped by\n(脳3), (脳1 as Baby, 脳2 as Toddler and Teen) (1% 脳3)\nCrafting\nDescription\nTransmute Beard Hair into Beefalo Wool.\n脳2 ( only)\nFilters\n(for ).\nMiscellaneous\n\"beefalowool\"\n鈥淚t smells like beefalo tears.鈥漒n鈥揥ilson\n鈥淗a! I stole his hair!鈥漒n鈥揥illow\n鈥淚 make clothes of hair-cow.鈥漒n鈥揥olfgang\n鈥淪omewhere, a beefalo is naked and cold.鈥漒n鈥揥endy\n鈥淓XTRUDED BEEFALO DISGUSTINGNESS鈥漒n鈥揥X-78\n鈥淟ong follicles harvested from the beefalo.鈥漒n鈥揥ickerbottom\n鈥淚t feels like my beard.鈥漒n鈥揥oodie\n鈥淚t smells like a barn.鈥漒n鈥揗axwell\n鈥淩adiating a musty smell.鈥漒n鈥揥agstaff\n鈥淚 d枚 l枚ve w枚olly things.鈥漒n鈥揥igfrid\n鈥淭hick fur.鈥漒n鈥揥ebber\n鈥淚t looks more like hair to me.鈥漒n鈥揥alani\n鈥淭he beast's loss is my gain.鈥漒n鈥揥arly\n鈥淐arries a musk wit' it.鈥漒n鈥揥oodlegs\n鈥淲OOL FROM ANY OTHER BEAST WOULD SMELL SWEETER鈥漒n鈥揥ilba\n鈥淏uddy hair鈥漒n鈥揥ormwood\n鈥淎 woolly projectile.鈥漒n鈥揥heeler\n鈥淪melly, but warm.鈥漒n鈥揥inona\n鈥淓x-beefalo鈥漒n鈥揥ortox\n鈥淔luffs.鈥漒n鈥揥urt\n鈥淪orry, beefalo.鈥漒n鈥揥alter\n鈥淭he beefalo will grow it back.鈥漒n鈥揥anda\nBeefalo Wool is an Item obtained by killing a Beefalo or聽a聽Baby Beefalo, by shaving a sleeping聽Beefalo with a Razor (by clicking them with a Razor held by the mouse cursor), or using a Brush on a Beefalo.聽It is used to make a Saddle, Winter Hat, Beefalo Hat, Puffy Vest, and Carpeted Flooring.\nBeefalo Wool also makes an excellent Fuel source for Campfires and Fire Pits. A small herd of Beefalo can easily keep a Fire Pit lit for days, and as the wool grows back, this is a good short term solution.\nThere are alternative methods of obtaining Beefalo Wool; harvesting a Tumbleweed, or befriending a Catcoon, as friendly Catcoons may give Beefalo Wool as a gift.\nWillow needs Beefalo Wool to craft Bernie. It is also required to craft Spinnerbait Lures and to complete the construction of the Royal Tapestry.\nBeefalo Wool can be crafted by Wilson if he got \"Transmute Icky II\"\n